myViz <- function (myGraph){
  visIgraph(myGraph, randomSeed = 11)  %>%
  visIgraphLayout(randomSeed = 11) %>%
  visNodes(
    font = list(size = 59),
    shape = "dot",
    color = list(
      background = "#0085AF",
      border = "#013848",
      highlight = "#FF8000"
    ),
    shadow = list(enabled = TRUE, size = 10)
  ) %>%
  visEdges(
    shadow = FALSE,
    color = list(color = "#0085AF", highlight = "#C62F4B")
  ) %>%
  visLayout(randomSeed = 11)
}
